ariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Croatian\n\nJosip is 39 years old, and lives in Split, Croatia. He studied at the maritime high school in Split and finished the Faculty of Maritime Studies at the University of Split. Soon after his degree, he started working on the sea and yachts, and his life and education grew around it. Josip holds a certificate Master of a ship up to 3000 GT, Yacht Master up to 500 GT, GMDSS certification, SSO certification.\nJosip is an easygoing person with a strong focus on providing a safe, secure and enjoyable environment for the guests at all time. Born in Split he often acts as a local guide for charter guests to ensure they truly immerse themselves in their Croatian charter experience."},{"name":"Durdica Borovic","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7646090758::vessel::d5cc4d69-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::642a5340-2cba-11f0-a1a2-bdf7036fb298/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Croatian\n\nAfter she graduated from the School of Economics in Split, Durdica began gaining experience in customer service, quickly developing a strong foundation in working with people. With over 10 years of experience in the hotel industry, Durdica has built a career as a housekeeper and cleaner. Her experience in high-standard hospitality, with attention to detail and guest-focused service, will apply in a dynamic yachting environment, where she can bring her dedication to a new level of service excellence.\nKnown for her cheerful and sociable nature, she brings excellent communication skills. She is well organized, flexible and practical. \n"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2350000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2350000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"High Season Charter Rate","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to"